Facebook post by Noorie Noor Ananta, 30 October 2016 (9 days before demonetization). Text: 'Today the next new challenge to my life hv knocked at my door. Yes yes ..year 2017 come come i m ready 8 (horse emoji) welcom. My Diwali Gift.' DECODED: Number '8' embedded in Diwali greeting. Horse emoji (Kalki's white horse) appears again. 'My Diwali Gift' = demonetization was announced near Diwali. 'year 2017 come come i m ready' = readiness for what follows. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Coded Signals — demonetization framed as a 'Diwali Gift' of cosmic transformation.